{"tid":1790840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【凍結星火】警昨午高調開記招拉人 4被捕人兩小時後已准保釋","createTime":"2019-12-20T09:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T10:38:36.000Z","uid":25468,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"26cdd70c58fdfd0507e23682888e94646f2b4671","tid":1790840,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:54:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191220/large/1576831921_ca28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191220%2Flarge%2F1576831921_ca28.jpg&h=c5607e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方昨午召開記者會，高調宣佈以「洗黑錢」罪名拘捕「星火同盟」（以下簡稱星火）3男1女，並凍結約港幣7,000萬元，但具體「洗黑錢」證據卻說不出一個所以然。星火今午4時許在facebook發帖，稱被捕人士早在昨晚7時左右已全部獲保釋離開警署，感謝各方關心。星火又強調該平台的被捕支援工作從沒受到影響，承諾會繼續全力支援因抗爭而被拘捕的人士。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，昨日警方開有關案件的記者會時間為下午5時15分，即4人僅僅在記者會後兩小時便獲保釋。<br />\n<br />\n直至今日下午5時許，警方才發新聞稿，交代被捕的3男1女已獲准保釋候查，須於明年一月中旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191220/60399738\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191220%2F60399738&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5faDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=483ca9bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191220%2F60399738&h=2b3ea5f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191220/60399738</a>"},{"pid":"e500e51944dbd9997a1053074bc5019bd4627b7f","tid":1790840,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:54:47.000Z","msg":"有鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1cce0fc85d56855efae1766256a73579c44fa1","tid":1790840,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:02:12.000Z","msg":"鳩拉左先 , 再開記招屈"},{"pid":"f4433fb61fd358626d34fc2ab5a61468db7de513","tid":1790840,"uid":271199,"like":2,"disl